        "version": "2026-07-19T19:12:36.330Z"
      }
    ],
    "commentsEnglish": "Book desc prints awj «أو عجم». The sayr's jawāb segāh / jawāb chahārgāh are entered as buzurk / māhūrān; the touched jawāb ṣabā has no app note name yet.",
    "commentsArabic": "",
