    "commentsEnglish": "The 9th ascending degree is printed نيم بوسليك; entered as jawāb nīm būselīk (jawāb intended). Book desc 8th prints ḥijāz ( أو جهاركاه ). In the descent, ḥijāz on dūgāh alternates with the ṣabā ending.",
