        "commentsEnglish": "Opens by performing maqām ḥijāz ascending and descending; after settling on dūgāh it turns to perform maqām iṣfahān, and its qarār ends on dūgāh according to iṣfahān's conditions — the reverse of maqām humāyūn's path.",
