    "commentsEnglish": "Scale deduced by cross-reference (no table in the book) — verify: the stated descent (ḥusaynī–nawā–chahārgāh–segāh–dūgāh–rāst) over a rāst-scale frame, as in dilkesh ḥūrān (p.40) which shares this sayr on ʿirāq.",
